        <updateDate>2013-04-03T21:53:11Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Charitable Driving Tax Relief Act of 2013 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide that volunteers who use their automobiles for the benefit of a charitable organization may exclude from their gross income reimbursements for their automobile operating expenses at the same level as business employees (i.e., 56.5 cents per mile in 2013).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
